OL,3,CMan jailed for 12 years after bottle
OL,4,Cattack on two train passengers
OL,6,FA man who launched a "wholly
OL,7,Fmurderous" attack on a train passenger
OL,8,Fwith a bottle has been jailed for 12
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FThomas Craig, who is 48 years old and
OL,12,Ffrom East Renfrewshire in Glasgow,
OL,13,Fattacked Aaron Nelson with a broken
OL,14,Fbottle on a train from Glasgow Queen
OL,15,FStreet to Perth on February 16 2025.
OL,17,FHe then attacked Nelson's friend Glen
OL,18,FLennon with the same bottle after he
OL,19,Ftried to intervene.
