OL,3,CMan jailed for 12 years after bottle
OL,4,Cattack on two train passengers
OL,6,FThe attack left Lennon with a wound
OL,7,Fnear his heart and he lost more than
OL,8,Ftwo litres of blood. Both victims, who
OL,9,Fare in their early twenties, were
OL,10,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
OL,12,FCraig was found guilty of the
OL,13,Fattempted murder of Glen Lennon and
OL,14,Fthe serious assault of Aaron Nelson in
OL,15,FNovember.
OL,17,FThe court heard that Craig had been
OL,18,Fdrinking alcohol for several hours and
OL,19,Fhad taken cocaine before the attack.
