OL,3,CMan jailed for 12 years after bottle
OL,4,Cattack on two train passengers
OL,6,FHe was handed an extended sentence on
OL,7,FMonday, comprising 12 years behind
OL,8,Fbars and three years of supervision
OL,9,Fupon release.
OL,11,FAt the High Court in Glasgow, the
OL,12,Fjudge called Craig's attack on the two
OL,13,Fmen "appallingly violent" and
OL,14,Fdescribed his assault of Lennon as "a
OL,15,Fwholly murderous attack".
OL,17,FHanding down his sentence, Lord
OL,18,FArthurson added: "Members of the
OL,19,Fpublic have every right to be able to
OL,20,Ftravel on public transport safely and
OL,21,Fwithout fear."
