OL,6,FCCTV footage released by British
OL,7,FTransport Police (BTP) in December
OL,8,Fshowed Craig charging down the
OL,9,Fcarriage and raising his arm to smash
OL,10,Fthe bottle down on one of the victims,
OL,11,Fbefore moving to a seat and changing
OL,12,Ffrom his blood-stained jumper into a
OL,13,Fclean hoodie.
