OL,3,CMan jailed for 12 years after bottle
OL,4,Cattack on two train passengers
OL,6,FTony Graham KC, representing Craig,
OL,7,Fsaid there was nothing he could say in
OL,8,Fmitigation but said his client has
OL,9,Fstruggled with drug and alcohol
OL,10,Faddiction and feels remorse over the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,F"He understands the damage he has
OL,14,Fdone, he understands the suffering he
OL,15,Fhas caused and he understands that
OL,16,Fthose short moments on that train will
OL,17,Flive with and probably haunt forever
OL,18,Fhis victims," he said.
