OL,6,F"This is a man who recognises he has
OL,7,Fdone wrong. This is a man who
OL,8,Frecognises the potentially devastating
OL,9,Fconsequences, averted in this case."
OL,11,FBTP Detective Inspector Marc Francey
OL,12,Fpreviously said: "Craig acted in a
OL,13,Ftruly despicable manner, violently and
OL,14,Frelentlessly attacking two men over a
OL,15,Fminor disagreement and causing
OL,16,Fcountless passengers on the train to
OL,17,Fpanic.
