OL,6,F"His indiscriminate and thuggish
OL,7,Factions could have resulted in far
OL,8,Fmore severe consequences, both for his
OL,9,Fvictims and for himself.
OL,11,F"It is thanks only to luck and to the
OL,12,Flifesaving work of the paramedics that
OL,13,FCraig hasn't been found guilty of
OL,14,Fsomething far worse."
OL,16,FHe added: "Violence on the railway is
OL,17,Futterly unacceptable and we will
OL,18,Frelentlessly pursue offenders like
OL,19,FCraig to ensure they face justice."
